Pawn Code Command Line Shell (PawnCLIS)
>> Features:
    * compilator,
        * package manager,
            * tool server.
>> Required Linux: 
    * Python3 - "sudo apt install python3"
        * pip python {urllib3} - "sudo apt install python3-pip", "pip install urllib3"
            * cURL - "sudo apt install curl"
>> Required Windows:
    * WSL/Git Bash - "scoop install extras/wslgit"
        * Python3 - "scoop install versions/python313"
            * pip python {urllib3} - "pip install urllib3"
                * cURL - "scoop install main/curl"